## Permitted Use

The only permitted use of artwork in this repository is:

1. Viewing on the official website (targz.shop)
2. Purchasing original pieces through the official shop
3. Sharing links to the official website

## Purchase

Original artworks are available for purchase at https://targz.shop

Purchasing an artwork transfers ownership of the physical piece only. Copyright and reproduction rights remain with the artist.

